Package xxl.core.indexStructures.builder.BPlusTree

The builder class for BPlusTrees.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BPlusConfiguration
    This implementation of IndexConfiguration base class allows to setup all requirements for building a BPlusTree.
    BPlusConfiguration.Creator
    A concrete implementation of IndexConfiguration for setting up the requirements of a BPlusTree according to your needs.
    BPlusConfiguration.Loader
    This class is used to reload a BPlusIndexedSet (wrapper for BPlusTree) from a previous session.
    BPlusTreeBuilder<E>
    A concrete implementation of IndexBuilder to easily create or restore an index with BPlusTree type.
    ManagedType
    To specify which data type is managed by a generic index structure use a subclass of this abstract base class.
    PrimitiveType
    Use this class if the index structure should use standard java objects.
    TupleType
    Use this class if the index structure should use Tuple objects.
